## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-102">O <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe é uma implementação concreta do resumo <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-102">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is a concrete implementation of the abstract <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ObjectCache> class.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-103">O <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe é semelhante para o ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class is similar to the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-104">O <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe possui muitas propriedades e métodos para acessar o cache será familiar se você tiver usado o ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-104">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has many properties and methods for accessing the cache that will be familiar to you if you have used the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-105">As principais diferenças entre o <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> e <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classes são que o <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe foi alterada para torná-lo utilizável por [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] aplicativos que não são aplicativos ASP.NET.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-105">The main differences between the <xref:System.Web.Caching.Cache> and <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classes are that the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has been changed to make it usable by [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] applications that are not ASP.NET applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-106">Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe não tem nenhuma dependência de `System.Web` assembly.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-106">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class has no dependencies on the `System.Web` assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-107">Outra diferença é que você pode criar várias instâncias do <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> classe para uso no mesmo aplicativo e na mesma <xref:System.AppDomain> instância.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-107">Another difference is that you can create multiple instances of the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class for use in the same application and in the same <xref:System.AppDomain> instance.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-108">O <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> não permitir que a classe `null` como um valor em cache.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-108">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> class does not allow `null` as a value in the cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-109">Qualquer tentativa de adicionar ou alterar uma entrada de cache com um valor de `null` falhará.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-109">Any attempt to add or change a cache entry with a value of `null` will fail.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-110">O <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> tipo não implementa *regiões de cache*.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> type does not implement *cache regions*.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-111">Portanto, quando você chama <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> métodos que implementam métodos base que contêm um parâmetro de regiões, não passe um valor para o parâmetro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-111">Therefore, when you call <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache> methods that implement base methods that contain a parameter for regions, do not pass a value for the parameter.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-112">Os métodos que usam o parâmetro de região todos fornecem um padrão `null` valor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-112">The methods that use the region parameter all supply a default `null` value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-113">Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> sobrecarga de método tem um `regionName` parâmetro cujo valor padrão é `null`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-113">For example, the <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.MemoryCache.AddOrGetExisting%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method overload has a `regionName` parameter whose default value is `null`.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-114">O exemplo a seguir declara uma referência à instância padrão do cache de memória.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-114">The following example declares a reference to the default memory cache instance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-115">A entrada de cache usa um <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> objeto para fornecer detalhes de remoção e vencimento para a entrada de cache.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-115">The cache entry uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.CacheItemPolicy> object to provide eviction and expiration details for the cache entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11b5c-116">Ele também usa um <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> objeto para monitorar o estado da fonte de dados (que é um arquivo) no sistema de arquivos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11b5c-116">It also uses a <xref:System.Runtime.Caching.ChangeMonitor> object to monitor the state of the source data (which is a file) on the file system.</span></span>  

```vb  
Private Sub btnGet_Click(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As EventArgs)   
    Dim cache As ObjectCache = MemoryCache.[Default]   
    Dim fileContents As String = TryCast(cache("filecontents"), String)   

    If fileContents Is Nothing Then   
        Dim policy As New CacheItemPolicy()   
        Dim filePaths As New List(Of String)()   
        filePaths.Add("c:\cache\example.txt")   

        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(New HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths))   

        ' Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents = File.ReadAllText("c:\cache\example.txt")   

        cache.[Set]("filecontents", fileContents, policy)   
    End If   

    Label1.Text = fileContents  
End Sub  
```  

```csharp  
private void btnGet_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)  
{  
    ObjectCache cache = MemoryCache.Default;  
    string fileContents = cache["filecontents"] as string;  

    if (fileContents == null)  
    {  
        CacheItemPolicy policy = new CacheItemPolicy();  

        List<string> filePaths = new List<string>();  
        filePaths.Add("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  

        policy.ChangeMonitors.Add(new   
        HostFileChangeMonitor(filePaths));  

        // Fetch the file contents.  
        fileContents =   
            File.ReadAllText("c:\\cache\\example.txt");  

        cache.Set("filecontents", fileContents, policy);  
    }  

    Label1.Text = fileContents;  
}  
```
